name: REBEL WITHOUT A CONDOM
description: REBEL WITHOUT A CONDOM, would have been an imaginary band had they ever banded. Taking their name as a wordplay pun from the famous 1955 film "Rebel Without a Cause" starring young heartthrob, James Dean. This Providence, Rhode Island trio's hayday was back in early 2000s as a noise rock band sounding somewhere between Stereolab and Arab on Radar. They formed at RISD (Rhode Island School of Design) and should have been part of Fort Thunder, but a love triangle of infidelity caused a falling out with the band and with Fort Thunder. The band only put out 1 EP in their short stint together.
